Homepage: https://github.com/dedshit/blutter-termux
Description: Flutter/Dart Binary Analysis and Reverse Engineering
 blutter is a tool for analyzing and reverse engineering Flutter/Dart
 binaries. Provides capabilities for extracting information and
 analyzing compiled Flutter applications.
